	<message label="305_01" attrib="00 00 00 00">Also!<delay20 /> D<tag a="50" b="2" /><colour id="1" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><colour id="65535" /> ist bereit, <delay8 />hm?</message>
	<message label="305_02" attrib="00 00 00 00">Also!<delay20 /> D<tag a="50" b="2" /><colour id="1" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><colour id="65535" /> ist bereit, <delay8 />hm?<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Und Platz in der Tasche hast du
